    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>Starting <strong>September 18, 2025</strong> Liferay has introduced the<strong> product experience management </strong>capability to better understand your administrative team’s needs and improve your experience with Liferay. As communicated back in September, a <strong>progressive rollout </strong>meant to validate these capabilities has been implemented. On February 12, 2026 the rollout reached 100% of Liferay Cloud customers (<strong>SaaS </strong>and <strong>PaaS</strong>).</p>\n\n<p><strong>What to Expect:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Direct Feedback:&nbsp;</strong>Your team can share feedback directly inside the product</li>\n\t<li><strong>In-App Support (phased):&nbsp;</strong>You'll begin to see personalized guides that help teams get more from key features</li>\n\t<li><strong>Faster Improvements:&nbsp;</strong>Usage insights will inform our roadmap so we can continuously enhance the product.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Administrators will see a <strong>cookie consent banner</strong> on first login after that date to manage preferences. If they accept, we’ll collect usage insights to improve the experience.</p>\n\n<p>We’re also updating our <a href=\"https://www.liferay.com/privacy-policy\">privacy policy</a> and <a href=\"https://www.liferay.com/cookie-policy\">cookie policy</a> to reflect these changes.</p>\n\n<p>This change does not impact <strong>performance, stability, or security</strong>. If you have any questions or would like to request to opt-out, please contact <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/\">Liferay Support</a> or your Account Manager.&nbsp;</p>"
      },
